Pantheon Lens

This is actually another interface family.

Interface	Borrowed From	Typical Transfer
Anthropomorphism	Humans	Intent, emotion, planning
Zoomorphism	Animals	Instinct, ecology, adaptation, behavior
Mechanomorphism	Machines	Precision, computation, modularity
Biomorphism	Living systems	Growth, development, self-organization
Theomorphism	Deities	Cosmic roles, transcendence, ideals

Each interface transfers a different kind of machinery.

