Generalizing the idea

Maybe there’s an umbrella term:

Morphic Interfaces

Interfaces derived from another class of being.

Subtypes:

* Anthropomorphic
* Zoomorphic
* Mechanomorphic
* Biomorphic
* Geomorphic (landforms)
* Hydromorphic (water behaviors)
* Mycomorphic (fungal behaviors)
* Astronomorphic (stars, galaxies, orbital dynamics)

Each imports different operators.

